snippet.title: Rendezvous with Rama Part 1 - Commodore 64
snippet.description: Graphical text adventure for the commodore 64.  It is about a large cylindrical spaceship that passes through the solar system (based on book by Arthur C Clarke).  Interestingly enough, but in real life on October 19, 2017, astronomers detected the first interstellar object travelling through our solar system (Oumuamua).  It passed through our solar system quickly so all we know is it is 5-10 longer than its width. Its also quite shiny.  We've never seen anything quite like it.  What could it be?
